data.description: Gorgeous Brick home on .18 acres in Tucson near DMAFB and close to shopping and bus lines. This property has a sparkling blue pool in the backyard that is fenced and ready to cool off in for the hot summers. 4 bedrooms and 1 full bath! This property has an un-permitted addition that adds a ton space to the home. There are is a beautiful open space and to living areas. Fireplace in the great room! Roof was recently recoated!
